@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rkklno(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.35 / wp.exp(tmp))
    v1 = wp.exp(v2)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp(0.49))
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = (tmp + (wp.exp(tmp + 0.16) / 0.44))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = ((0.56 * (v1 + 0.26 / v2 + 0.80)) + tmp)
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.34) * ((v1 + 0.34 * v0 + 0.59) + wp.cos(tmp + 0.30)))
    data[tid] = v0
